<p>A predawn landslide triggered by torrential rain hit a village in West Bandung regency on Indonesia’s Java island, killing at least seven people and leaving dozens of residents unaccounted for. Rescue teams have been searching the affected area for people still missing as daylight operations continued. The incident adds to a difficult start to the year for Indonesia’s disaster responders after recent deadly floods and landslides elsewhere in the country.</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/GbJeYl-UyRnDuIHTCe2QXOf0PvdCMzHyAFQ68xh-1wrjN5JGPRrFNZWVxku90QyD0Uk9D-tfhLWgQlqU2g-QVASaTfjG-c0a1m-h95vl3kjIrUXnLJ9HgWbYms7HvJvaInXoMjcRQcJNpKU' alt='Illustrative image used by ABC News for its report on the West Java landslide.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Early-morning strike: Officials said the slope collapsed at around 2:30am local time, damaging homes in the village.</li><li>Agency updates: Indonesia’s national disaster agency (BNPB) provided the casualty and missing figures through spokesperson Abdul Muhari as assessments continued.</li><li>Search conditions: The BBC reported rescue teams were combing the West Java village for 83 people still unaccounted for.</li><li>Toll variation: ABC News reported at least eight deaths and more than 80 people missing, reflecting shifting counts as information comes in.</li><li>Wider context: Al Jazeera noted the landslide came weeks after floods and landslides in Indonesia’s west that reportedly killed more than 1,000 people.</li></ul><blockquote>A landslide occurred in West Bandung regency, West Java province, in the early hours of Saturday, killing seven people. - Abdul Muhari</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Indonesia’s national disaster agency (BNPB): The agency reported the landslide followed heavy rainfall and said its initial count showed seven people killed and more than 80 missing as of late morning. (<a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/southeast-asia/article/3341090/7-killed-82-missing-indonesian-landslide-west-bandung-java'>South China Morning Post</a>)</li><li>Rescue teams: Responders continued searching the village for people still unaccounted for, according to BBC reporting on ongoing operations. (<a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c87r53y4dx0o'>BBC</a>)</li><li>Al Jazeera reporting: The outlet framed the incident as part of a broader pattern of recent rain-related disasters in western Indonesia following earlier deadly floods and landslides. (<a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2026/1/24/seven-dead-82-missing-after-landslide-in-indonesias-bandung'>Al Jazeera</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/landslide-indonesias-java-island-kills-8-people-leaves-129514688'>Landslide on Indonesia&#x27;s Java island kills at least 8, leaves dozens missing</a> - abcnews.go.com</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/southeast-asia/article/3341090/7-killed-82-missing-indonesian-landslide-west-bandung-java'>7 killed, 83 missing in Indonesian landslide in West Bandung, Java</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/indonesia-landslide-death-toll-january-24-2026/article70545568.ece'>At least seven dead, 82 missing in Indonesian landslide, disaster agency says</a> - thehindu.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2026/1/24/seven-dead-82-missing-after-landslide-in-indonesias-bandung'>Seven dead, dozens missing after landslide in Indonesia’s West Bandung</a> - aljazeera.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c87r53y4dx0o'>Indonesia landslide kills 7, dozens more missing</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://www.abc.net.au/news/2026-01-24/indonesia-landslide-west-bandung-west-java-province/106265558'>Seven people are killed and 82 others are missing after a landslide at West Bandung Regency, West Java, Indonesia.</a> - abc.net.au</li></ul>